PMID== 6256880
TI  == [susceptibility of anaerobic bacteria to cefoxitin (author's transl)].
AB  == nine strains of clostridium perfringens type a and 10 strains of bacteroides fragilis s. spec. fragilis, recently isolated from blood culture, were tested for their cefoxitin susceptibility. the mic for clostridium perfringens ranged from 0,6 to 5 mg/l and 1,2 to 10 mg/l for bacteroides fragilis. in most cases, the mbc were identical with the mic for clostridium perfringens, but for bact. frag. there was a difference of 2 dilutions in their mbc. cefoxitin activity was not modified by a variation in inoculum density.
TIHT== 
